'''宫廷爱情'''是[[中世纪|中世纪]][[欧洲|欧洲]]高贵的[[骑士|骑士]]向贵族女士表达[[爱|爱]]与钦佩的概念。<ref name=middleages>{{cite web |url=http://www.middle-ages.org.uk/courtly-love.htm |title=Courtly love |publisher=Middle Ages.com |date=2007-05-16 |accessdate=2010-01-18 |archive-date=2013-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020182921/http://www.middle-ages.org.uk/courtly-love.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>一般来说，宫廷爱情是秘密的，发生在[[贵族|贵族]]成员之间。<ref name=simpson>{{Cite web |url=http://condor.depaul.edu/dsimpson/tlove/courtlylove.html |title=Simpson, David L., "Chivalry and Courtly Love", DePaul University, Chicago, Illinois, 1998 |accessdate=2013-08-09 |archive-date=2013-07-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130704184134/http://condor.depaul.edu/dsimpson/tlove/courtlylove.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>它一般没有夫妻关系老练。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://cla.calpoly.edu/~dschwart/engl513/courtly/courtly.htm |title=Schwartz, Debora B., "Courtly Love", California Polytechnic State University, accessed 2010-01-18 |access-date=2013-08-09 |archive-date=2010-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100106034322/http://cla.calpoly.edu/~dschwart/engl513/courtly/courtly.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>11世纪末期，宫廷爱情发生于[[阿基坦|阿基坦]]、[[普罗旺斯|普罗旺斯]]、[[香槟_(行省)|香槟]]、[[勃艮第公國|勃艮第公國]]等地。<ref>Francis X. Newman, ed. (1968). ''The Meaning of Courtly Love'', vii.</ref>

